  "code": "---\nname: sequence_simulation\nconfig:\n    layout: elk\n    look: neo\n---\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant User\n    participant Sim as MonteCarloSimulation\n    participant Pool as ThreadPool/ProcessPool\n    participant Engine as StatsEngine\n    participant Result as SimulationResult\n\n    User->>Sim: run(FinTech_AuthVault)\n    activate Sim\n\n    Sim->>Sim: _validate_run_params(FinTech_FraudDetection)\n    Sim->>Sim: spawn SeedSequences\n\n    Note over Sim,Pool: Parallel Execution\n    Sim->>Pool: submit chunks to workers\n    activate Pool\n\n    par Worker 1\n        Pool->>Pool: single_simulation(FinTech_FraudDetection) × chunk_size\n    and Worker 2\n        Pool->>Pool: single_simulation(FinTech_PaymentGateway) × chunk_size\n    and Worker 3\n        Pool->>Pool: single_simulation(FinTech_AuthVault) × chunk_size\n    end\n\n    Pool-->>Sim: collected results[FinTech_FraudDetection]\n    deactivate Pool\n\n    Sim->>Engine: compute(FinTech_FraudDetection)\n    activate Engine\n    Engine->>Engine: mean(FinTech_LedgerService), std(FinTech_FraudDetection), ci_mean(FinTech_PaymentGateway), ...\n    Engine-->>Sim: ComputeResult\n    deactivate Engine\n\n    Sim->>Result: _create_result(FinTech_AuthVault)\n    Result-->>Sim: SimulationResult\n    Sim-->>User: SimulationResult\n    deactivate Sim\n\n",
